  "mainOuterHtml": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n    <div class=\"container cf\">\n\n      <div id=\"shopify-section-template--26857879863369__main\" class=\"shopify-section page-section-spacing\">\n  <div class=\"article-image article-image--large align-center \">\n    \n      <div class=\"page-header page-header--with-background img-fill  page-header--padded-huge\">\n        \n\n<img src=\"//salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=2048\" alt=\"True sustainability is quality that lasts a lifetime.\" width=\"2048\" height=\"921\" loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"//salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=425 340w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=600 480w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=925 740w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=1225 980w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=1500 1200w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=1750 1400w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=2000 1600w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=2400 1920w, //salt-yard.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/Unrecorded-store_2048x_7cc6a889-ae04-429d-90f5-0ddbe8a437fe.jpg?v=1614946936&amp;width=2560 2048w\" class=\"theme-img\">\n<div class=\"text-overlay text-overlay--inline\"></div>\n        \n      </div>\n    \n  </div>\n\n\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"page-header reading-width\">\n        <h1 class=\"majortitle\">True sustainability is quality that lasts a lifetime.</h1>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n\n\n<div class=\"article article--main\">\n  <div class=\"container container--reading-width\">\n\n    <div class=\"rte cf spaced-row\">\n      <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<p>When it comes to thinking sustainably across the whole business, we believe that few come close to Unrecorded. More than a mere label, we think that sustainability is a doing word. To be sustainable is to last more than a lifetime.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0848/3828/files/sus1.jpg?v=1614251719\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Nothing is wasted. We always use 100% of the fabric that is made for us. Brands with seasons create waste through overstock and unused materials. We produce neither.</p>\n<p>Unrecorded fabrics are developed specifically for us and we only produce quality apparel that lasts.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0848/3828/files/sus2.jpg?v=1614251790\"></p>\n    </div>\n\n    \n    <div class=\"lightly-spaced-row cc-animate-init cc-animate-in\" data-cc-animate=\"\">\n      <div class=\"social-share flex items-center\">\n        <p class=\"social-share__heading\">Share</p>\n        <ul class=\"social inline-flex flex-wrap\"><li>\n      <a class=\"social__link flex items-center justify-center\" href=\"//twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=True%20sustainability%20is%20quality%20that%20lasts%20a%20lifetime.&amp;url=https://salt-yard.myshopify.com/blogs/magazine/true-sustainability-is-quality-that-lasts-a-lifetime\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Tweet on X\">\n        <svg class=\"icon\" fill=\"currentColor\" role=\"presentation\" focusable=\"false\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" viewBox=\"1 1 22 22\">\n  <path d=\"M1